    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tannıs Deenâs Elijasti- ba/ Jojadus/ Joanana un Jad- duus/ tappe tee Lewiti uhsrak- stiti/ ka tee augstakee Tehwi: Ka arri tee Preesteri appaksch tahs Waldischanas Darrijusa ta Persexa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Lewja Behrui/ tee augstee Tehwi/ tappe Laiku- Grahnata rakstiti/ lihds Joa- nana/ Elijasiba Dehta Deen- nahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Wirfneeki to Lewitu bija/ Asabijus/ Serebijus/ un Jesuns/ Kadnitêka Dehls; un winnu Brahti bija kahrt win- xeem/ ka tee stahwetu un teiktu/ pehz to Bauslibu ta Deewa Wihra Dahwida/ weenu Sar- gaschann pehz ohtru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Matanijus/ un Bukba- kius/ Obadijus/ Mesullams/ Talmons/ Akuds/ tee btja Wahrtu-Sargi; Sargaschann turredaunt pee teem Wahrtu Sleeksneeti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee bija Jojakima/ ta Dehta Jesuns/ ta Dehta Zada- ka Deenâs: Un Neennijus/ ta\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Seimnes-Walditaja/ un Es- ta Preestera/ ta Raksta-Ma- taja Deenâs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pee tahs Eefive- schanas tahs Jerusalemes Mi- ra/ mekleja tee tohs Lewitus wistahn winnu Weetahin/ tee tohs uhs Jerusaleini wes- ka tee turretu Eefwehtichani Preeku/ un ar Pateiffchanu/ ar teizamahn Dseefmahin/ ar Pułkstenischeem/ un ar S- ma-Stabulehn/ un ar Ko- lehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Dseedataju Beh- tappe fapulzinati/ tiklabbi teem Klaijumeem apkahrt Je- salemi/ ka no teem Netow- Zeemeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Gilgata Namn- un no teem Gebas Tihrunee- un no Asinaweta. Jo tee Di- dataji bija tohs Zeeinus apka- Jerusalemi uhstaisijchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fchêihstijahs tee Pr- steri un Lewiti/ pehz to ichêih- ja tee tohs Landis/ un ta- Wahrtis/ un to Muhri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad weddu es tahs Ju- da Wirfneekus uhs to Muh- un litke diwi leelus Pateik- nas Pułkus/ un tee gahje pa la- bas Rohkas us to Muhri li- tahm Suhdu-Wahrtim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz teem gahje Osaju- un weena Pułfe to Juha Wi- neeku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Asartjus/ un Esru- un Mesullams.\n"
